Rock, Paper, Scissors, Implementation in Scratch


if player chooses rock:
    computer chooses rock -> DRAW!
    computer chooses scissors -> PLAYER WINS!
    computer chooses paper -> COMPUTER WINS!

if player chooses paper:
    computer chooses paper -> DRAW!
    computer chooses rock -> PLAYER WINS!
    computer chooses scissors -> COMPUTER WINS!

if player chooses scissors:
    computer chooses scissors -> DRAW!
    computer chooses paper -> PLAYER WINS!
    computer chooses rock -> COMPUTER WINS!
